                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.504/87</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consul <persName type="from">Dawson</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Tampico</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-04-30T13:00:00-06:41">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 30, 1917, 1 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Immediate question at issue has been adjusted satisfactorily as a result naval
                    intervention but strike spreading. Demonstrations may be expected to-morrow.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dawson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
